```

**Should be:**
```css
font-family: "jaf-bernino-sans-comp", sans-serif;
font-weight: 800;
font-style: normal;
```

This matches the working implementation used throughout the vioverse-refactor codebase. The font is already being loaded correctly via the Adobe Typekit link, but we're just using the wrong font-family name.

